text: Karl Neuner (16 January 1902 - 20 March 1949) was a German skier. He competed in the Nordic combined event at the 1928 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1902 births Category:1949 deaths Category:German male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of Germany Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 1928 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Garmisch-Partenkirchen
